                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18000917-9-defend94 t18000917-9-punish37"></join>
               DEATH
            </rs>. (Aged 19.)</p>
               <p>Stevens, <rs id="t18000917-9-verdict38" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18000917-9-verdict38" type="verdictCategory" value="notGuilty"></interp>
               NOT GUILTY
            </rs>.</p>
